high_descs: Turn left, walk straight, turn left towards oven.
Turn right at oven, go straight.
Pick up coffee mug, place into sink.
Pick mug back up, go towards coffee maker.
Place coffee mug under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Grab coffee mug, clean, put it back under machine.

high_descs: Turn left, left again and then right until you are standing in front of the cooker.
Pick up the cup that is in the coffee machine.
Turn to your left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, wash it and remove it from the sink
Turn right again and walk back to the coffee machine
Put the clean cup back in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Take the dirty cup from the coffee machine, wash it, then put it back in.

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the sink.
Clean the mug in the sink.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug in the coffee machine.
